gmsniff and ccsniff are the shipped observability CLIs at bin/gmsniff.js and bin/ccsniff.js (mirrored at gm-starter/bin/). gmsniff reads .gm/exec-spool/.watcher.log and ~/.claude/gm-log/<date>/plugkit.jsonl with flags --embed-failures, --recall-misses, --recall-scores, --classifier-rejects, --memory-leverage, --recall-modes, --table-drops, --discipline-sigil-ignored, --since <Ns|Nm|Nh|Nd>. ccsniff reads ~/.claude/projects/**/*.jsonl with --git-discipline (raw git push, force, commit-without-push) and --learning-xref (joins transcript turns to rs_learn events). Both are pipe-friendly with no external deps.